<body>
  <header>
    <h1>Support - AutoComment GPT</h1>
    <p>Thank you for using our Chrome extension to generate LinkedIn comments with AI.</p>
  </header>

  <section>
    <h2>Support</h2>
    <p>For any questions, contact us at: <a href="mailto:autocomment.supp@gmail.com">autocomment.supp@gmail.com</a></p>

    <h2>Privacy Policy</h2>
    <p>AutoComment GPT is committed to respecting users' privacy.</p>

    <h2>Data Collected</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Email address provided during secure payment via Stripe</li>
      <li>User identifier (userId) generated to associate credits with each user</li>
    </ul>
    <p>No other personal data is collected. We do not collect your name, messages, or browsing activity.</p>

    <h2>Use of Data</h2>
    <p>Data is used exclusively to:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Link credits to your account</li>
      <li>Enable credit recovery even after browser changes</li>
    </ul>
    <p>We do not sell, share, or transfer your data to third parties.</p>

    <h2>Storage & Security</h2>
    <p>Data is securely stored in our database. Payments are processed via Stripe, a PCI-DSS certified platform. We never store your credit card information.</p>

    <h2>Your Rights</h2>
    <p>You can request the deletion of your data (email and userId) at any time by contacting us at: <a href="mailto:autocomment.supp@gmail.com">autocomment.supp@gmail.com</a></p>

    <h2>Credits</h2>
    <p>Your credits are automatically linked to the email used during payment. If you switch browsers, click on "Recover My Credits" to restore them.</p>
  </section>

